        <para id="id1168923667420">Now, use the symbols to tell the story!</para>
        <para id="id1168923820246">As soon as you know the story in music, you may read the story a second time and decide where you must play loudly and where softly. The further away Thunder and Lightning are sent, the softer the sound; the angrier the people become, the louder the sound!</para>
